    <criterion testable="true">AI trigger failure doesn't fail check-in</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Logging records AI trigger attempt</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    Fire-and-forget pattern: use _ = Task.Run(...) or queue to background service.
    Don't await the AI operation in the check-in request path.
  </notes>

